Name: Elems
About the game: Elems is an arcade logic game and its goal is to collect the Orb of Life Shards, scattered across 32 levels in 4 zones: Hellish, Icy, Stone and Water zone. While playing, Imp Guardian (the main hero) has to collect all Orb Shards on the level to proceed to the next one. Features : 4 zones 32 levels About thousand Orb of Life Shards to collect Gravity, Teleports, Energo Barriers Rockfalls! Play and think!
